The paper deals with algorithms for solving the k-Dimensional Matching problem and the Exact Cover by k-Sets problem, which are both combinatorial optimization problems. These problems are commonly studied in the sub-fields of computer science such as data structures (cs.DS), computational complexity (cs.CC), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), computational geometry (cs.CG), and graph theory (cs.GT). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
